##spDataVersion:	1
##Title:	The Peschito Syriac New Testament
##Abbreviation:	TPSNT
##Information:	The Peschito Syriac New Testament by J.W. Etheridge, comprising:  The Syrian Churches: their Early History, Liturgies, and Literature. With a literal Translation of the Four Gospels, from the Peschito, etc. 1846  and  The Apostolical Acts and Epistles fromt he Peschito or Ancient Syriac: to which are added, the remaining epistles and the Book of Revelation, after a later syrian text, etc. 1849.
